Pan's Labyrinth;;91;;95;;R;;In 1944 Spain young Ofelia (Ivana Baquero) and her ailing mother (Ariadna Gil) arrive at the post of her mother's new husband (Sergi López), a sadistic army officer who is trying to quell a guerrilla uprising. While exploring an ancient maze, Ofelia encounters the faun Pan, who tells her that she is a legendary lost princess and must complete three dangerous tasks in order to claim immortality.;;Fantasy,War,Drama;;Guillermo del Toro;;2006;;Sergi López,Maribel Verdú,Ivana Baquero,Álex Angulo,Doug Jones,Ariadna Gil,Federico Luppi,Roger Casamajor,Manolo Solo;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/pans_labyrinth